\[(C + 0.16) + C = 1.20\]  
\[2C + 0.16 = 1.20\]  
\[2C = 1.04\]  
\[C = 0.52\]

Then:  
\[P = 0.52 + 0.16 = 0.68\]

The probability of visiting a physical therapist is 0.68.

